prodNameC: 協克抗可萃取核抗原自體免疫抗體試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1. Microscope slides (10 slides) with antigen- coated strips:
nRNP, Sm, SS-A, SS-B, Scl-70, Jo-1
2. Positive control (1x 0.2 mL)
IgG, human
3. Negative control (1x 0.2 mL)
IgG, human
4. Enzyme conjugate (1x 0.5 mL)
Alkaline phosphatase-labeled anti-human IgG (goat), 10x concentrate
5. Sample buffer (1x 60 mL)
6. Wash buffer (2x 100 mL)
10x concentrate
7. Substrate solution (1x 4.0 mL)
Nitroblue
tetrazolium / 5-bromo-4-chloroindolyl-phosphate (NBT/BCIP)
8. Test instruction (1 leaflet)
applicantAddr: 台北市大安區復興南路2段157號5樓之3
efficacy: 本產品提供一定性的體外檢測法，藉以測定血清或血漿中nRNP, Sm, SS-A, SS-B, Scl-70, Jo-1等6種抗原的IgG抗體。
